title: BRIEF-Ultra Clean Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.60
text:
Feb 21 (Reuters) - Ultra Clean Holdings Inc:
* ULTRA CLEAN ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER AND FISCAL YEAR 2017 FINANCIAL RESULTS
* Q4 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.59
* Q4 REVENUE ROSE 42.6 PERCENT TO $248.9 MILLION * SEES Q1 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.56 TO $0.63
* SEES Q1 2018 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.52 TO $0.59 * SEES Q1 2018 REVENUE $275 MILLION TO $290 MILLION * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.60 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.60, REVENUE VIEW $245.9 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.63, REVENUE VIEW $261.1 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
